org.dhbw.geo.backend

Class BackendController

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dhbw.geo.backend.BackendController

  • public class BackendController
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Oliver on 18.06.2015. This class exposes methods to access the backend. A fence is defined as a DBFence object and a fence group as a DBConditionFence object.
